# React Native 패턴

- 함수형 컴포넌트 + TypeScript strict
- `StyleSheet.create` co-located, 색상은 `constants/theme.ts` 토큰만 사용
- `app/` 화면: default export (Expo Router). 재사용 UI는 `components/` named export
- 200줄 초과 시 `components/{domain}/`로 분리
- `app/`·`components/`에서 Supabase client 직접 import 금지

```tsx
// ✅ app/walk/active.tsx
import { WalkMap } from '@/components/walk/WalkMap';
import { useWalkTracker } from '@/hooks/useWalkTracker';

export default function WalkActiveScreen() {
  const { elapsedSec, distanceMeter } = useWalkTracker();
  return <WalkMap distanceMeter={distanceMeter} />;
}
```
